    public ResponseEntity<ConvertedDatatablesData<EquipmentLubrication>> EquipmentsItemEquipmentLubricationsThymeleafController.datatablesByIdsIn(@RequestParam("ids") List<Long> ids, DatatablesColumns datatablesColumns, GlobalSearch search, DatatablesPageable pageable, @RequestParam("draw") Integer draw) {
        
        Page<EquipmentLubrication> equipmentLubrications = getEquipmentLubricationService().findAllByIdsIn(ids, search, pageable);
        long totalEquipmentLubricationsCount = equipmentLubrications.getTotalElements();
        ConvertedDatatablesData<EquipmentLubrication> data =  new ConvertedDatatablesData<EquipmentLubrication>(equipmentLubrications, totalEquipmentLubricationsCount, draw, getConversionService(), datatablesColumns);
        return ResponseEntity.ok(data);
